mindmap
  root((Merritrade Platform))
    Trading Web (User Frontend)
      eKYC Onboarding
        Upload Identity Card
        Auto-Scan & Verification
      Trading Engine
        View Real-time Forex/Binary Charts
        Place Orders (Forex/Binary)
        View Order History
      Tournament Hub
        Join Upcoming Tournaments
        View Ranking Boards
        Export Personal Order History
      Support & Disputes
        Submit Complaints to BTC
        View Notifications
    Admin Portal (Management Frontend)
      Tournament Management
        CRUD Tournaments
        Configure Ranking Criteria
      User Management
        Monitor Suspicious Activity
        Ban / Unban Traders
        Manage eKYC Approvals
      System Exports
        Export Global Tournament Rankings
        Export Mass Order Histories
    Backend Microservices & Cronjobs
      Hasura GraphQL Engine
        Rapid Data Aggregation
      Socket.io Real-time Layer
        Live Price Broadcasting
        Instant Client Disconnect (Bans)
      Precision Cron Schedulers
        T-3 / T-1 Marketing Mailers
        Auto-Close Open Orders at T-0
        Ranking Recalculation Engine
      Asynchronous Workers
        Heavy Excel/CSV Generation (Export)
        Identity Card OCR Processing (national-card)
